Package org.concordion.cubano.driver.web

Support for interacting with web browsers via Selenium WebDriver.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasePageObject<T extends BasePageObject<T>>
    Provides core functionality for pages objects using the page object factory pattern.
    Browser
    A wrapper around Selenium WebDriver to make it easier to open and close a specific browser regardless of whether that browser is running locally or remotely.
    ChainExpectedConditions
    Designed to work with WebDriverWait when you have multiple condition to check on a page.
    PageComponent
    Encapsulate a block of html elements on a page.
    PageHelper
    Helper class that allows PageObject and PageComponent to share functionality.
    PageReadyConditions
    Provides expected conditions to check that a page has completed any ajax requests.
    RemoteHttpClientFactory
    Allows WebDriver to connect to a Selenium grid through a proxy without requiring a tunnel to the provider.
    SeleniumEventLogger
    Listens for WebDriver events and logs them.
    SeleniumScreenshotTaker
    Takes screenshots of the system under test.
